## Steps
The first thing we need to do to start developing for Android is to install CodeWorks for Android 1R4, which will 
ensure that you have all the required programs and code needed to deploy to Android devices.
In the following section, we will cover how you can get CodeWorks for Android 1R4 installed on your development PC.


